An API(Application Programming Interface) is a set of commands, functions, protocol, and objects
that we can use to create software or interact with an external system.
Eg. jQuery API(APIs to create software)
Tinder ( Apis to Interact with external system)


API
-> Endpoint
-> Paths
-> Parameters
-> Authentication

